# Monthly crawl of all configured sources (ΦΕΚ, ΥΠΕΝ, ΤΕΕ, ...).
# Runs the 3rd of each month at 03:00 UTC — after the National Printing
# House typically finishes publishing the previous month's issues.
0 3 3 * * python -m crawler.main

# Weekly staleness sweep - flags public KB documents whose last_verified_at
# is missing or older than 6 months, for the super admin's manual review
# queue (GET /admin/stale-documents). Monday 04:00 UTC, after the sweep
# would have run against whatever the monthly crawl last touched.
0 4 * * 1 python -m crawler.staleness
